name: SKYCAT
description:
Cat vs Mouse! It's kawaii shoot'em up!

Mice were everywhere in Japan in 2020 ...Because it was a mouse year!
However, some have pursued mice since mythological times to stop it!
He couldn't become the Zodiac because he was fooled by the mouse!
A cat has just flew away with a Taiyaki in hand to defeat the mouse!

Game Features

Volumeful
ARCADE 5Stage + MISSION 48Stage x 5Level!

Cuteful
Cat customization!
